"title": "9024: death, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9024: death, spiritual",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A condition in this life of alienation from God because of sin. It leads ultimately to the “second death”, the permanent separation of unbelievers from God.</p>\n<h2>Spiritual death means alienation from God in this life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:3\">EPH 2:1–2:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:21\">COL 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:22\">MAT 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13\">COL 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual death is a result of Adam's sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:15-Rom5:16\">ROM 5:15–5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a></p>\n<h2>Symptoms of spiritual death</h2>\n<h3>Spiritual ignorance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:16\">MAT 4:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:2\">ISA 9:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:79\">LUK 1:79</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8\">EPH 5:8</a></p>\n<h3>A mind controlled by the sinful nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:8\">ROM 8:5–8:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:36\">PRO 8:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:12\">PRO 14:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:25\">PRO 16:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:16\">PRO 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:18\">EPH 4:18</a></p>\n<h3>Unbelief</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:12\">1JN 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>Living in sinful pleasures</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:13\">LUK 15:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:6\">1TI 5:6</a></p>\n<h3>Acting in ways that lead to death</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:1\">HEB 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14\">HEB 9:14</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual death leads ultimately to the ``second death''</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:11\">REV 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:6\">REV 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:14\">REV 20:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a></p>\n<h2>A church may be spiritually dead</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:1\">REV 3:1</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Deliverance from spiritual death is only through Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:1-Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:1–37:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:24\">LUK 15:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:32\">LUK 15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24-John5:25\">JHN 5:24–5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:3-Rom6:4\">ROM 6:3–6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:13\">ROM 6:13</a></p>",
